{"id":441504,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":3,"day":22}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"76","ytitle":"","mtitle":"扁担","ftitle":"","authors":["虞光华"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"虞光华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小扁担，话不多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吱哑吱哑爱唱歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百里路，十里坡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里雨里笑呵呵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑呵呵，来唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得日落西山坡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“先别夸咱脾气好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比起咱队长还差得多。”"}]}